meta.name: Fair City
meta.description: The day-to-day dramas of the community who live and work in the fictional north Dublin suburb of Carrigstown.

videos.overview: Zak warns a furious Sash she needs to change tack with James. Meanwhile JJ, eyes on the prize, watches from the shadows. Emma goes to war with Ger.

videos.title: Tue 11 Apr 2017
videos.overview: Niamh makes a decision about her future with Marcus, and Ciaran caves under the pressure of his double life. Meanwhile, Nikki sets her sights on Jake, who remains at odds with Ama.

videos.title: Thu 20 Apr 2017
videos.overview: The fallout from Paul and Niamh's conflict has disastrous consequences.

videos.title: Thu 27 Apr 2017
videos.overview: Ciaran lures Emmet into a harrowing game of cat and mouse as Katy's life hangs in the balance. A devastated Farrah is left without Ciaran's support as she struggles to cope with her loss. Niamh and Paul stumble across crucial information as their feud with Wayne and Orla escalates. Sash conceals her true feelings when she realises her relationship is at risk.

videos.title: Tue 2 May 2017
videos.overview: Rose provokes Caoimhe's ire by spurning Tommy's help with Katy's anniversary campaign. A fragile Farrah is smothered with love by her family, but will Heather takes things too far? Eoghan and Debbie worry about Emmet's mental state. While Emmet is pushed towards the edge as Katy's captor plays mind games with him.

videos.title: Thu May 4 2017
videos.overview: Ciaran gets a sick pleasure out of forcing Emmet to carry out an appalling act that devastates the O'Brien family. Rose's forgetfulness piques Caoimhe's interest. Farrah warns her family to stay out of her life. An increasingly erratic Ciaran promises Katy that her captivity will end very soon.

videos.title: Sun May 7 2017
videos.overview: Emmet is close to breakdown as Ciaran's demands get dangerous. Debbie and Eoghan fear for Emmet's mental health when he creates a major scene at the vigil for Katy. Caoimhe's concerns about Rose grow. Ciaran gives Emmet a life or death choice.

videos.title: Sun May 14 2017
videos.overview: Emmet agrees to sacrifice himself. He is horrified at his discovery when he seeks help from Ciaran. Debbie and Eoghan fear the worst when Emmet disappears.

videos.title: Sun May 14 2017
videos.overview: Debbie is in overdrive as she worries about Emmet. Farrah loses it with Heather when Ciaran drags up the past to keep Heather distracted. Meanwhile, Ciaran gives Emmet a terrifying ultimatum.

videos.title: Tue May 16 2017
videos.overview: Emmet is forced to face the ugly truth of his past actions. Rose worries about her memory lapses but keeps it to herself, as Heather takes drastic action to stop Farrah going away with Ciaran.

videos.title: Wed May 17 2017
videos.overview: Ciaran, stressed over Emmet and Katy, is now confronted with a suspicious Farrah and Debbie. As Rose, distracted with worry over Emmet, raises suspicions about her health. Meanwhile, a disorientated Katy tries to come to terms with her new surroundings. A shocking accusation by Heather threatens to bring Ciaran's world crashing down.

videos.title: Thur May 18 2017
videos.overview: Ciaran, trying to buy time, is forced with a difficult decision. Hughie meanwhile begins to believe that Heather's accusations against Ciaran may be true. Damien reluctantly leaves Rose in charge of Saoirse, with worrying consequences. Farrah declares her love for Ciaran.

videos.title: Sun May 21 2017
videos.overview: When Ciaran threatens Emmet's life, Katy is forced to take drastic action. Farah must face the awful truth about Ciaran while the O'Briens hope she can help reunite them with Katy. Damien lashes out when Rose's confusion puts little Saoirse at risk.

videos.title: Tue May 23 2017
videos.overview: The O'Briens have their hopes dashed as it seems they are further than ever to getting Katy home. Farrah struggles to process Ciaran's betrayal but comes under suspicion as Ciaran's accomplice. Charlie and Cass help Damien make peace with Rose.

videos.title: Wed May 24 2017
videos.overview: As Garda attention turns to Emmet, Farrah receives a disturbing phone call. Ciaran makes a devastating decision.

videos.title: Thu May 25 2017
videos.overview: Suspicion turns on Farrah. Eoghan tries to hold the O'Brien family together as they wait for news from the Guards.

videos.title: Sun May 28 2017
videos.overview: The investigation turns up some bad news for Farrah. There is trauma for the O'Briens as the details of Ciaran's murder plan hits home.

videos.title: Tue May 30 2017
videos.overview: As the Garda investigation closes in, Farrah takes the initiative. But has she made everything worse?

videos.title: Wed May 31 2017
videos.overview: Farrah, aided by Alannah, confronts the true horror of Ciaran's actions. Jake and Ama struggle to resolve their differences.

videos.title: Thu Jun 1 2017
videos.overview: Despite her attempts to maintain a brave face, Farrah, overcome with guilt, finally breaks down. Jake is furious when he discovers Ama has been discussing their relationship behind his back. Is there still hope for them?

videos.title: Tue Jun 6 2017
videos.overview: As Ellie freaks at the prospect of being interviewed by Gardai, journalists camp on Farrah's doorstep. An unexpected arrival causes tension between Kerri-Ann, Decco and Sash, Laura. Cracks begin to show in the recently patched up relationship of Jake and Ama. Meanwhile, war is declared as Jane and Nicola take sides in the Callum, Oisin feud.

videos.title: Wed Jun 7 2017
videos.overview: As Farrah struggles to get on with her life, Kevin pushes for answers about Ellie and Heather. Kerri-Ann inadvertently causes trouble for Jake and Ama. Left holding the baby, will Decco finally find his parenting instincts? Meanwhile, the claws are out between Nicola and Jane.

videos.title: Thu Jun 8 2017
videos.overview: Kevin forces Heather to unlock some deeply upsetting memories. Sash worries Nikki won't cope in a B&B with two small babies. Oisin's plot to get revenge on Callum backfires. Ama gives Jake some devastating news.

videos.title: Thu 25 August 2022
videos.overview: Pete is determined to support Doug, little realising how vengeful Ray is, while Tommy struggles to help a rejected and dejected Anto. Cass and his crew finally make a viable plan to accomplish their sit-in at the site, but with Renee and Damien both suspicious, is it too late?

videos.title: Fri 26 August 2022
videos.overview: As they bring their baby home, Doug implores Erica to let the past go, but can she really forgive him? Anto grows hopeful when he and Sharon manage to have a civilised talk, while Mairead warns Damien.

videos.title: Sun 28 August 2022
videos.overview: When his hopes of fixing his marriage are stonewalled by Hayley, Anto strikes a financial blow at Sharon, while Damien plans to take on James alone, but conceals it from Mairead. Fearing his actions have driven Erica away permanently, Doug is pushed closer to the edge

videos.title: Tue 30 August 2022
videos.overview: Doug is unable to live with his conscience any longer and horrifies Erica by taking drastic action, while a bitter Anto points the finger at Carol as the root of all his problems. When a discovery on the building site brings work to a standstill, James isn't long in tracking down the culprit

videos.title: Thu 01 September 2022
videos.overview: Anto takes advantage of Tommy's goodwill when his desperation hits a new low, while Maria is made to feel part of the community despite her blunder. With Doug's life seemingly falling back into place, Ray sets his sights on him

videos.title: Fri 02 September 2022
videos.overview: An excited Mondo makes big plans for Melanie's return, while Anto runs out of options as he continues to alienate his nearest and dearest. Losing his grip on the build, a desperate James promotes Cian to the role of project manager

videos.title: Sun 04 September 2022
videos.overview: Sharon is devastated when Anto's lies land him in hospital, while Mondo prepares a romantic gesture for Melanie's return, but will it go to plan? Damien wonders how far a pressured James is prepared to go

videos.title: Tue 06 September 2022
videos.overview: Faced with his demons, Anto finally admits the truth, but will it be enough to stop him gambling? James continues to make dangerous cost-cutting decisions on site, while Mondo is gutted when he gets a call from Melanie.

videos.title: Thu 08 September 2022
videos.overview: James is shellshocked when an unexpected visitor turns up on site, while Hayley puts pressure on Anto to make the right decision about his future. But will he listen? A distraught Mondo blames Alex for his break-up

videos.title: Fri 09 September 2022
videos.overview: Juliet asks for help as Mondo continues his downward spiral, while Rafferty sees first-hand the mess James has made of the development. Nora makes waves when she reveals her compensation proposal.

videos.title: Tues 02 January 2024
videos.overview: Under pressure from Carol, will Hayley admit she has the evidence to get James arrested? Fergal continues to manipulate Dean and extracts damming information from him.

videos.title: Thurs 04 January 2024
videos.overview: Anto has a surprising offer for Hayley. Greg decides he needs to distract an over familiar Steoaway from Jess. Fergal's twisted plan hits an unexpected snag.

videos.title: Sun 07 January 2024
videos.overview: Fergal's attempt to connect with other people blows up in his face, but Dean let's slip some crucial information to Vicky. Hayley assuages James's suspicions and gets him onside.

videos.title: Tues 09 January 2024
videos.overview: Dean inadvertentlygives Fergal a way to exact full punishment. Hayley revels in the success of her revenge plan. Bob's future is threatened by Paul's feudwith Hughie.

videos.title: Thurs 11 January 2024
videos.overview: Fergal exacts the ultimaterevenge on Dean. Hayley refuses to walk away from James. Hughie punishes Bob for wronging him. Juliet calls Steo out on his intentions towards Jess.

videos.title: Sun 14 January 2024
videos.overview: Greg laments his skills as a father. An overstretched Kira brings Ruby on board to help with the fashion show. Orla is tempted by Lenny's offer to reconnect.

videos.title: Tues 16 January 2024
videos.overview: When it all gets too much for Dean, he makes a momentous decision. Coming to Ruby's defence, Victor riles Kira up.

videos.title: Thurs 18 January 2024
videos.overview: Dean turns the tables on Fergal but is unprepared for what follows. Ruby walks Kira into an awkward situation. Orla's offended when Mairead tries to matchmake.

videos.title: Sun 21 January 2024
videos.overview: Dean's desperation leads to a stay of execution from Fergal. Kira is forced to eat humble pie with Victor while Orla teaches Lenny a lesson.

videos.title: Tues 23 January 2024
videos.overview: Desperate to replace the scammed money, Melanie invents a bogus invoice but how suspicious is Hughie? Kira is charmed when Victor voices his support for her fashion show.

videos.title: Thurs 25 January 2024
videos.overview: Kira's fashion show leads to some unexpected passion as Melanie's money woes hit a wall with Maxine. Zoe is thrown by Alex's moving in plans.

videos.title: Sun 28 January 2024
videos.overview: Maxine requests an audit of all of Joan's invoices to Rafferty from Melanie.Kira has a hard time hiding her guilt from Mondo and Babs.Cass and Leo make peace with Georgie.

videos.title: Tues 30 January 2024
videos.overview: Cass is on a mission to make amends with Georgie. Melanie goes to drastic lengths to make back the money she owes. Juliet despairs when Mondo is determined to help Alex.

videos.title: Thurs 1 February 2024
videos.overview: Dean's fear of what Fergal might do next redoubles when Gar returns home. Melanie is in for a shock when she meets Joan's new client.

videos.title: Sun 4 February 2024
videos.overview: While trespassing in Gar's place, Fergal makes a startling discovery. Melanie is freaked when Hughie hints he knows who stole his car.

videos.title: Tue 06 February 2024
videos.overview: Georgie attempts to improve Anna's love life. Melanie sabotages Hughie and Zoe. Fergal increases the pressure on Dean.

videos.title: Thu 08 February 2024
videos.overview: Melanie faces a crisis of conscience. Dearbhla is appalled at Gar's revelation about Fergal. Dean has a fateful confrontation with Fergal.

videos.title: Sun 11 February 2024
videos.overview: Dean is freaked to get a chilling phone call from Fergal. Sharon counsels Erica not to fall out with Doug over tensions in the house.

videos.title: Tue 13 February 2024
videos.overview: A troublemaking Fergal drops a bombshell to Gar before the engagement party. Hayley sets her plan to take down James in motion.

videos.title: Thu 15 February 2024
videos.overview: Hayley's plan to rig the raffle and blame James crashes and burns. Pete hides his sadness and celebrates Erica and Doug's thrilling news.

videos.title: Sun 18 February 2024
videos.overview: Mairead says something she regrets when she gets into a heated exchange with DamienHayley worries when she's unable to get in touch with James.Dearbhla considers her future with Gar.

videos.title: Tue 20 February 2024
videos.overview: Hayley is stunned when an outraged Carol exposes Hayley's deception. Is this the end for Hayley and James? Erica is undermined by an increasingly unpredictable Pete.

videos.title: Thu 22 February 2024
videos.overview: Hayley and James have a day of reckoning as their past misdeeds come under scrutiny. Carol, intent on getting justice, takes matters into her own hands.

videos.title: Sun 25 February 2024
videos.overview: Carol's revenge plot is interrupted by the arrival of Fr. Liam. Doug questions whether pain management is an issue for Pete. Mairead grows suspicious of Orla.

videos.title: Tue 27 February 2024
videos.overview: Liam begins to piece together Carol's involvement with Aidan. Gwen's party proves a success, but she may have a regret. Mairead sets a trap for Orla. Erica and Doug confront Pete.

videos.title: Thu 29 February 2024
videos.overview: Jacinta fumes with Fergal. Fergal snares Dean in his plan to get back on side with her. Liam continues to accuse Carol. Pete struggles. Gwen has Mondo in her sights.

videos.title: Sun 03 March 2024
videos.overview: Dearbhla and Gar discover Vangirl's true identity. Erica and Doug struggle to manage as Pete suffers withdrawals Sash sets a trap for Gwen. Carol rejects Liam's olive branch.

videos.title: Tue 05 March 2024
videos.overview: Dearbhla and Gar force Dean's hand. A desperate Doug medicates Pete. Kira sets ground rules before another tryst with Victor. Hayley and James park their feelings.

videos.title: Thu 07 March 2024
videos.overview: To Dean's horror, Fergal sidesteps justice. Kira uses Mondo to teach Victor a lesson. Pete and Doug agree to trick Erica. Liam's heartfelt apology leaves Carol rattled.

videos.title: Sun 10 March 2024
videos.overview: Fergal is fearful that Jacinta will turn on him. Dolores determines to find out what's going on with Mairead And Orla. James threatens to reveal all to Rafferty.

videos.title: Tue 12 March 2024
videos.overview: Jacinta has finally had it with Fergal. Jess struggles to keep Steo at bay. Dolores is shocked to learn Orla's secret. Damien is on for getting payback on Rafferty.

videos.title: Thu 14 March 2024
videos.overview: It's finally all too much for Dean: time for desperate measures. Liam is knocked back as Rafferty is happy to play dirty. Orla and Paul try a new approach: civility.

videos.title: Tue 19 March 2024
videos.overview: Gar is horrified to learn from Jacinta what's really been going on at home with Fergal. As Rafferty celebrates his win over the charity, Liam discovers he has something to hide.

videos.title: Thu 21 March 2024
videos.overview: Jacinta connives to get an oblivious Dearbhla onside. Doug is alarmed when Pete decides to return to work.

videos.title: Sun 24 March 2024
videos.overview: Doug is wracked with guilt when Pete's addiction spins out of control. A vengeful Jacinta declares war on Joan. Jess is unsettled when Steo edges closer into their lives.

videos.title: Tue 26 March 2024
videos.overview: Hughie determines to be there for Doug, as the pressure of Pete's addiction becomes too much for him. Kira and Victor have a close call when Mondo arrives to the office.

videos.title: Thu 28 March 2024
videos.overview: Fergal's threats escalate to a dangerous level. Jess tries to fight her feelings for Steo while Pete is confronted with the truth about his addiction.

videos.title: Sun 31 March 2024
videos.overview: Steo agrees to forget about the kiss, but can Jess? Anto's protective behaviour rubs Sharon up the wrong way. Hayley's unsure about working with James again.

videos.title: Tue 02 April 2024
videos.overview: Carol ignores Nora's words of caution and takes a leap of faith with Liam. Greg lands Jess with an ultimatum about Steo. Sharon fears that Anto plans to stay put.

videos.title: Thu 04 April 2024
videos.overview: Hayley worries as Liam finds discrepancies in Rafferty's raffle. Jess, torn between Steo and Greg, follows her heart. Anto promises Sharon he'll move out.

videos.title: Sun 07 April 2024
videos.overview: Ruby is stunned when Jess confides in her that she's in love with Steo.Sharon is pleasantly surprised by Anto's gung-ho attitude to apartment hunting, but Gwen is suspicious.Liam shows his hand to James and Hayley, asking for the youth caf to be reinstated in exchange for his silence regarding the rigged raffle.

videos.title: Tue 09 April 2024
videos.overview: Liam's battle with Rafferty reaches the endgame. Mel wants to make amends to Zoe. Babs gives Victor a difficult task. Jess gets a rude awakening.

videos.title: Thu 11 April 2024
videos.overview: Greg clashes with Steo. Mel is spooked when a figure from her past reappears. Rafferty takes revenge on Hayley.

videos.title: Sun 14 April 2024
videos.overview: An unwelcome visitor at Melanie's fundraiser drops a bombshell to Zoe. James & Hayley thrash out their differences and come to a decision about their future.

videos.title: Tue 16 April 2024
videos.overview: Mel might convince Zoe to believe her lies but what about Hughie and Alex? Will Mel confess? Jess defends Steo but secretly wonders if she has made a mistake.

videos.title: Thu 18 April 2024
videos.overview: Haley enlists Liam to distract Rafferty, but her and James's plot to oust him goes up in smoke when Emma arrives and drops a bombshell.

videos.title: Sun 21 Apr 2024
videos.overview: Hayley surprises Emma with a tempting proposal. A fuming Babs is determined to discover why Kira won't work with Ruby. Liam is shocked to find Fergal living in near squalor. Ray leads a worker's revolt against an overbearing Tommy

videos.title: Tue 23 Apr 2024
videos.overview: Tommy makes a horrifying discovery. Jacinta reveals Fergal's toxic wrongdoings to Liam. Babs is shocked by Ruby's plans for her future. Emma enjoys her power position over James and Rafferty

videos.title: Thu 25 Apr 2024
videos.overview: Kira and Victor's affair comes close to discovery by Babs. Fergal begs Liam to give him a second chance. James and Hayley are concerned by Rafferty and Emma's closeness. Damien is shocked by Carol's betrayal of Tommy

videos.title: Sun 28 Apr 2024
videos.overview: Tommy bears the brunt of Carol's accusations, but causes even more hassle when he tries to shut it down. Georgie's curiosity about the murder victim leads to conflict with Garda Ronan. Buckley mentors Fidelma as he leads the investigation. Orla begins to suspect something between Victor and Kira

videos.title: Thu 2 May 2024
videos.overview: Buckley is hopeful when there is a major breakthrough in the case. Tommy leads the community in remembrance of the unknown victim. Sharon helps to broker peace between Georgie and Ronan. Orla confronts Kira about her affair with Victor

videos.title: Sun 5 May 2024
videos.overview: When Georgie and Ronan hit it off over a drink, Ronan misreads the signals. Kira insists to Orla that she isn't catching feelings for Victor, but bad news has her seeking comfort in his arms. The community is shocked to learn that the murder victim may be one of their own

videos.title: Thu 9 May 2024
videos.overview: Georgie and Ronan clear up their misunderstanding and agree to take things slow. Victor ends the affair with Kira, unaware of an eavesdropping Ruby. A DNA test confirms Damien's darkest fears

videos.title: Sun 12 May 2024
videos.overview: Mairead makes a horrifying discovery at Laura's wake. Damien and Mark drift further apart. Ruby struggles to keep her secret, raising alarm bells for Babs. Jess and Steo are off to a rocky start. Despite objections, a fearful Pete increases security at the garage

videos.title: Tue 14 May 2024
